### GET - alle Rezepte (am Anfang leer)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recipes

### POST - neues Rezept anlegen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/recipes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Chicken & Rice",
  "category": "Chicken",
  "area": "American",
  "instructions": "Reis kochen. Hähnchenbrust anbraten. Servieren.",
  "caloriesPerServing": 450,
  "proteinG": 35,
  "carbsG": 55,
  "fatG": 8
}

### GET - ein Rezept per ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recipes/1

### GET - nicht-existente ID (sollte 404 geben)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recipes/9999

### PUT - Rezept aktualisieren
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/recipes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Chicken & Rice (Updated)",
  "category": "Chicken",
  "area": "American",
  "instructions": "Reis kochen. Hähnchenbrust marinieren, dann anbraten.",
  "caloriesPerServing": 470,
  "proteinG": 40,
  "carbsG": 55,
  "fatG": 10
}

### POST - Validierungsfehler (Titel fehlt → 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/recipes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "Beef",
  "caloriesPerServing": 500
}

### DELETE - Rezept löschen
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/recipes/1

### DELETE - bereits gelöscht (sollte 404 geben)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/recipes/1

###
### --- MealPlan Endpoints ---
###

### GET - alle Pläne (am Anfang leer)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans

### POST - neuer Plan
POST http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cut Phase November",
  "description": "Gewichtsreduktion vor Weihnachten",
  "goal": "CUT",
  "startDate": "2025-11-01",
  "endDate": "2025-11-30"
}

### POST - zweiter Plan
POST http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lean Bulk Januar",
  "description": "Vorsichtiger Aufbau",
  "goal": "BULK",
  "startDate": "2026-01-01",
  "endDate": "2026-03-31"
}

### GET - alle Pläne
GET http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans

### GET - nur CUT-Pläne (Filter über @RequestParam)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans?goal=CUT

### GET - by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans/1

### PUT - aktualisieren
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cut Phase November (verlängert)",
  "description": "Doch noch eine Woche dran",
  "goal": "CUT",
  "startDate": "2025-11-01",
  "endDate": "2025-12-07"
}

### POST - Validierungsfehler (name fehlt → 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goal": "MAINTAIN",
  "startDate": "2026-01-01",
  "endDate": "2026-06-30"
}

### POST - Validierungsfehler (goal fehlt → 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Plan ohne Ziel",
  "startDate": "2026-01-01",
  "endDate": "2026-06-30"
}

### GET - ungültiger Enum-Wert (sollte 400 geben)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans?goal=INVALID

### DELETE
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans/1

###
### --- PlannedMeal Endpoints (mit verketteten Tests) ---
###

### Schritt 1: Recipe anlegen, ID merken
POST http://localhost:8080/api/recipes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Chicken & Rice",
  "category": "Chicken",
  "instructions": "Reis kochen, Hähnchen anbraten.",
  "caloriesPerServing": 450,
  "proteinG": 35,
  "carbsG": 55,
  "fatG": 8
}

> {%
    client.global.set("recipeId", response.body.id);
%}

### Schritt 2: MealPlan anlegen, ID merken
POST http://localhost:8080/api/meal-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Cut Plan",
  "description": "Tests",
  "goal": "CUT",
  "startDate": "2025-11-01",
  "endDate": "2025-11-30"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("mealPlanId", response.body.id);
%}

### Schritt 3: PlannedMeal anlegen, die beide referenziert
POST http://localhost:8080/api/planned-meals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-11-05",
  "mealType": "LUNCH",
  "mealPlanId": {{mealPlanId}},
  "recipeId": {{recipeId}}
}

> {%
    client.global.set("plannedMealId", response.body.id);
%}

### Schritt 4: GET - alle Mahlzeiten anzeigen (sieh die nested Response!)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/planned-meals

### Schritt 5: GET - nur Mahlzeiten dieses Plans
GET http://localhost:8080/api/planned-meals?mealPlanId={{mealPlanId}}

### Schritt 6: GET - nur Mahlzeiten am 5.11. dieses Plans
GET http://localhost:8080/api/planned-meals?mealPlanId={{mealPlanId}}&date=2025-11-05

### Schritt 7: PUT - Mahlzeit von LUNCH auf DINNER ändern
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/planned-meals/{{plannedMealId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-11-05",
  "mealType": "DINNER",
  "mealPlanId": {{mealPlanId}},
  "recipeId": {{recipeId}}
}

### Schritt 8: POST mit ungültiger mealPlanId (sollte 400 geben)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/planned-meals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-11-05",
  "mealType": "BREAKFAST",
  "mealPlanId": 99999,
  "recipeId": {{recipeId}}
}

### Schritt 9: POST mit fehlender mealType (Validierung → 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/planned-meals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2025-11-05",
  "mealPlanId": {{mealPlanId}},
  "recipeId": {{recipeId}}
}

### Schritt 10: DELETE - PlannedMeal entfernen
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/planned-meals/{{plannedMealId}}